** Getting the Next Link(s) for Review

=GET /review/next=

?n=1

*** Response

404 when no more links are available for review

A list of up to n link-to-review objects:

<literal><pre><code>
[
{"linkNumber": integer
,"foreign": "string"
,"foreignLang": "string"
,"foreignLanguage": "string"
,"familiar": "string"
,"familiarLang": "string"
,"familiarLanguage": "string"
,"linkType": "linkword"|"soundalike"|"association"
,"linkword": "string"}
]
</code></pre></literal>

Note that linkword will be =null= for linktypes other than "linkword".

