** Mark a Link as Reviewed

<code>POST /review/</code><literal><em>linkno</em></literal>

*** Parameters

grade ::
  a floating point number from 0 to 1
  0 indicates complete failure to recall the meaning of the word
  1 indicates perfect recall of the meaning of the word
  The floating point value allows you to use a continuous grading scale. However, we recommend that you use the discrete grades: 0.0 0.2 0.4 0.6 0.8 and 1.0.

time ::
  an integer
  The number of milliseconds that recall took. This should be measured from the moment the foreign word is displayed to the learner until the learner requests the display of the translation.

*** Response

empty HTTP 200 OK on success, HTTP 500 error message on failure

